commit message: Add support for delegates with JSONObject outputs
Add views for MAC vendor and MAC type
String values for MAC Vendor and MAC Type
Initial implementation of an AsyncTask to get additional MAC information
Since the API gives us an array with pretty much always one JSON object just convert it to a JSON object manually since using JSONArray would require bumping the minimum API level to 19
Provide endpoint for the UI to call GetMacInfoAsyncTask
Show fetching... for the MAC vendor and type while its actually being fetched
Get additional MAC info right away when the activity is launched and handle displaying it on the UI along with any potential issues
If the hostname can't be fetched for some reason let the user know
